%% Reviewed 2026-04-09 for B-071 to keep cross-surface scope escalation and budget truth explicit in Atlas.
flowchart TB
  subgraph Evidence["1. Raw Evidence Inputs"]
    Timeline["Compass timeline rows<br/>event kind, touched scopes, fanout"]
    Local["Local changes<br/>path class, generated vs source, governance-only"]
    Plans["Radar and plan truth<br/>status, execution tasks, verified completion"]
    Proof["Proof State<br/>warning posture, blocker frontier, unsafe closeout"]
    Readouts["Delivery and operator readouts<br/>stale authority, conflict, claim guard"]
  end

  subgraph Ladder["2. Scope Signal Ladder"]
    Features["Deterministic feature vectors<br/>fanout, generated-only, governance-only,<br/>verified local, active execution, warning, blocker"]
    Rules["Shared rung rules<br/>R0 suppressed_noise<br/>R1 background_trace<br/>R2 verified_local<br/>R3 active_scope<br/>R4 actionable_priority<br/>R5 blocking_frontier"]
    Caps["Caps and rollups<br/>governance-only <= R1<br/>broad fanout <= R1<br/>generated-only -> R0<br/>child R5 dominates parent"]
    Signal["scope_signal payload<br/>rung, token, reasons, caps,<br/>promoted_default, budget_class"]
  end

  subgraph Budgets["3. Provider-Neutral Budget Classes"]
    None["none<br/>no fresh expensive work"]
    Cache["cache_only<br/>reuse and deterministic only"]
    Fast["fast_simple<br/>cheap local/simple reasoning only"]
    Escalated["escalated_reasoning<br/>fresh provider or heavier reasoning allowed"]
  end

  subgraph Consumers["4. Cross-Surface Consumers"]
    Compass["Compass<br/>scope dropdowns, scoped timelines,<br/>promoted workstreams, narration budgets"]
    Radar["Radar<br/>default operational ordering and focus chips"]
    Registry["Registry<br/>component ordering and operator readout priority"]
    Atlas["Atlas<br/>active-workstream pills and default promotion"]
    Shell["Dashboard / shell / chatter<br/>compute budget gating and escalation order"]
  end

  Timeline --> Features
  Local --> Features
  Plans --> Features
  Proof --> Features
  Readouts --> Features
  Features --> Rules
  Rules --> Caps
  Caps --> Signal

  Signal --> None
  Signal --> Cache
  Signal --> Fast
  Signal --> Escalated

  Signal --> Compass
  Signal --> Radar
  Signal --> Registry
  Signal --> Atlas
  Signal --> Shell

  Note["One additive contract decides visibility, promotion, and budget.<br/>Raw source truth stays exhaustive; default operator focus becomes selective."]:::note
